1.0.0.name: wordpress/its-a-girl
1.0.0.description: Created by pure-essence.net. It's a Girl is a responsive theme designed for baby girl blogs. It features a front page center widget area under high resolution that's ideal for a gallery widget. It supports Jetpack infinite scroll.
